                                '<div style="color: #ff6b6b; font-weight: 600; font-size: 11px; margin-bottom: 8px;">贪心算法决策逻辑：</div>' +
                                '<div style="color: #a0c4e8; font-family: monospace; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.6;">' +
                                    'best_stack = find_shortest_stack()<br>' +
                                    '<span style="color: #7a9aba;">// 只看当前高度，不考虑未来</span>' +
